{
  "stem": "4122.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If I was unconscious or what, I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I heard every shot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[CRYING] And then they started [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to pull us out, outside, by our legs, to pull out-- outside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was in the middle of the night, dark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] when everybody was out from there, [SOBBING] they took-- they started searching us because some of us had always something like sewed in, and some kind of jewelry or money or whatever.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because in the time from the war, so we always-- like my father used to say, we shall-- everybody shall have something in case we can-- if we get catched, then we shall have something for ransom money.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] searched everyone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know-- I was thinking of if I wanted to know if somebody is still alive or not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was trying to hear if somebody will say something or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was a girl who gave a cough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, somebody is living there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he bring her head-- and they were [SOBBING] tapping her like [CRYING] you hear in the butcher store.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[SOBBING] So I decided not to say that I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I wonder if they'll put me alive into the grave or what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't know what they will do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- [CRYING]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had already a grave with those other people somewhere because they came with a wagon-- a big wagon-- [CRYING] and they put us in the-- in this wagon.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- I was the first one put in the wagon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the wagon had like such white-- it had like a ladder.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
